{
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "title",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 480,
      "y": -200,
      "width": 640,
      "height": 150,
      "color": "6",
      "text": "# How an AI Agent Works (2026)\n\nThe loop: a frontier model plans, calls tools over MCP, observes results, updates memory, and repeats \u2014 all under governance."
    },
    {
      "id": "loop",
      "type": "group",
      "x": 320,
      "y": 20,
      "width": 880,
      "height": 250,
      "color": "6",
      "label": "The agent loop"
    },
    {
      "id": "user",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -40,
      "y": 70,
      "width": 260,
      "height": 120,
      "color": "4",
      "text": "## User / Task\n\nA goal stated in natural language."
    },
    {
      "id": "model",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 360,
      "y": 70,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 150,
      "color": "1",
      "text": "## Model (the brain)\n\nClaude Opus 4.7 / GPT-5.5 / Gemini 3.1 \u2014 plans, reasons, picks the next action."
    },
    {
      "id": "mcp",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 800,
      "y": 60,
      "width": 360,
      "height": 170,
      "color": "5",
      "text": "## MCP \u2014 the USB-C for AI\n\nOpen standard (Nov 2024). One protocol for tools, resources & prompts. 9+ SDKs, ~2000 registry servers, 70+ clients."
    },
    {
      "id": "tools",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 800,
      "y": 320,
      "width": 260,
      "height": 130,
      "color": "2",
      "text": "### Tools\n\nFunctions the agent calls \u2014 search, code, even this JSON Canvas server."
    },
    {
      "id": "data",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1100,
      "y": 320,
      "width": 260,
      "height": 130,
      "color": "2",
      "text": "### Resources\n\nFiles, databases & APIs exposed for context."
    },
    {
      "id": "memory",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 360,
      "y": 320,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 130,
      "color": "3",
      "text": "## Memory\n\nPersistent facts across turns \u2014 the model writes & reads memory files."
    },
    {
      "id": "orchestration",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 340,
      "y": 500,
      "width": 360,
      "height": 140,
      "color": "5",
      "text": "## Orchestration\n\nMulti-agent: a planner spawns sub-agents in parallel (Grok's 4-agent ensemble, Anthropic Managed Agents)."
    },
    {
      "id": "governance",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 800,
      "y": 500,
      "width": 360,
      "height": 140,
      "color": "1",
      "text": "## Governance\n\nPermissions, sandboxing, Origin checks & audit logs \u2014 agency kept under control."
    },
    {
      "id": "transports",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1230,
      "y": 70,
      "width": 250,
      "height": 130,
      "color": "5",
      "text": "### Transports\n\nstdio (local) \u00b7 Streamable HTTP (remote)."
    },
    {
      "id": "src",
      "type": "link",
      "x": -40,
      "y": 320,
